text:
This was all amazing, Gura. Thank you for putting in so much work on all of this over the past who even knows how long. The song especially is so INCREDIBLE; you talked about wanting to take the time with your first song to really make it special and fitting for YOU, and just from that preview I can already tell it's PERFECT. The payoff for everything was amazing, and I hope it was everything you'd hoped for as well.

And I hope today shows you that really, truly, you are dearly loved and adored. No matter how messy, or unprepared, or emotional, or inadequate or anything you feel...you are wonderful, beautiful, and incredibly special. You make this world a much brighter place being exactly who you are.

Get some good rest, Gura. You've earned it. I hope my letter in the book (it is an actual book you'll get eventually by the way, in case there was any doubt) can give you another smile whenever you read it. Love you. <3 Otsusame~

(Manager-san, you're a serious hero for reminding her about the PDF. Thank you so much.)
